<li id="cite_note-Festinger,_L._1957-1"><span class="mw-cite-backlink">^ <a href="#cite_ref-Festinger,_L._1957_1-0"><sup><i><b>a</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Festinger,_L._1957_1-1"><sup><i><b>b</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Festinger,_L._1957_1-2"><sup><i><b>c</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Festinger,_L._1957_1-3"><sup><i><b>d</b></i></sup></a> <a href="#cite_ref-Festinger,_L._1957_1-4"><sup><i><b>e</b></i></sup></a></span> <span class="reference-text">Festinger, L. (1957). <i>A Theory of Cognitive Dissonance</i>. California: Stanford University Press.</span>
